{
  "stem": "20711.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know, he may received money for it, or he did it on his goodness.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I really can't say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But my brother was together with my father for a couple of months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed with this aunt and uncle just for a short while because it's a very funny thing happened in the same time at that little village.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a group of the intellectuals of the town-- the priest, one of the teacher, the head of the town, and the head of the police organization, which was not police, but we called that the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what the English translation, but in a books, I heard-- I read it [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know if I say it correctly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was the organization we had in our town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on every weekend-- usually on Sunday night-- these four men would come together and play card.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the priest, the Catholic priest, was especially very close friend of us and admired my father for his religious tolerance and also my mom.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He never called it against my mom of changing religion, and he always showed a special affection to our family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And during playing card, one of the guy who was the head of the town, he happened to mention, oh, this Schvarcz family is just too wise.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They are getting away with murder.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I fix their wagon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know where Otto is, but I find out where he studied.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I made all kind of an arrangement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And tomorrow morning-- early morning, 5:00 or 6:00 in the morning-- the police, the Miskolc police is heading to that house where she is staying.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
